      <title>加拿大劳工委员会要求铁路员工复工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/canada-labor-board-orders-rail-employees-back-to-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大一个独立法庭命令该国两大铁路公司的工人重返工作岗位，并接受具有约束力的仲裁，以解决困扰北美供应链的争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/canada-labor-board-orders-rail-employees-back-to-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 22:27:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟警告：红海油轮起火可能引发生态灾难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/burning-red-sea-oil-tanker-risks-ecological-disaster-eu-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟驻红海海军周六表示，一艘载有原油的船只在红海遭袭击后起火，可能导致严重的生态灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/burning-red-sea-oil-tanker-risks-ecological-disaster-eu-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 22:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西圣保罗州发生多起山火，火灾数量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/brazil-s-sao-paulo-state-burns-amid-record-number-of-wildfires</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圣保罗州是拉丁美洲最大经济体最富裕的地区，由于低湿度和酷热，该州正面临创纪录数量的火灾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/brazil-s-sao-paulo-state-burns-amid-record-number-of-wildfires</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 22:01:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国财政部长斯塔默警告称，变革需要时间，并将责任归咎于“腐败”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/uk-s-starmer-to-warn-change-will-take-time-blame-rot-at-core</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默将在 8 月 27 日发表的演讲中警告称，英国政府承诺的改革需要时间，情况可能先恶化再改善，同时他还将批评英国首相从保守党手中继承下来的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/uk-s-starmer-to-warn-change-will-take-time-blame-rot-at-core</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳主要反对党指定 100 亿美元计划提振经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/ghana-s-main-opposition-earmarks-10-billion-plan-to-lift-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳主要反对党表示，如果赢得 2024 年 12 月的选举，将根据所谓的“大力推动”计划投资 100 亿美元来推动增长并扩大经济规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/ghana-s-main-opposition-earmarks-10-billion-plan-to-lift-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 18:04:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国官员谴责犹太教堂爆炸事件后的反犹太行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/french-officials-denounce-antisemitic-acts-after-synagogue-blast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国即将离任的总理加布里埃尔·阿塔尔呼吁该国反击反犹太主义，此前当局对法国南部一座犹太教堂附近的爆炸事件展开了恐怖主义调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/french-officials-denounce-antisemitic-acts-after-synagogue-blast</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 17:18:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国宇航局选择 SpaceX 来营救被困太空的宇航员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/spacex-selected-by-nasa-to-rescue-astronauts-marooned-in-space</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克的 SpaceX 公司将于明年使用其一艘太空舱将被困在国际空间站的宇航员带回地球，这对其竞争对手波音公司来说是一次新的挫折，同时也引发了人们对 NASA 未来将如何为轨道实验室配备人员的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/spacex-selected-by-nasa-to-rescue-astronauts-marooned-in-space</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 17:13:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称库尔斯克行动正在按计划进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/zelenskiy-says-kursk-operation-is-going-according-to-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，乌克兰跨越边境进入俄罗斯库尔斯克地区的行动正在按照计划进行，旨在阻止莫斯科占领东北部城市苏梅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/zelenskiy-says-kursk-operation-is-going-according-to-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 13:10:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯派团队前往开罗了解停火谈判最新进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/hamas-sending-team-to-cairo-for-update-on-cease-fire-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯称，一个代表团将于周六晚前往开罗，了解旨在实现加沙停火的谈判的最新进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/hamas-sending-team-to-cairo-for-update-on-cease-fire-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 10:42:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及会谈前夕，以色列空袭造成加沙数十人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-24/dozens-killed-in-strikes-in-southern-gaza-as-preparations-for-cease-fire-talks-move-forward</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开罗（美联社）——卫生工作者周六称，以色列空袭造成加沙南部至少三十名巴勒斯坦人死亡，此时包括哈马斯代表团在内的官员聚集在邻国埃及举行高层停火会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-24/dozens-killed-in-strikes-in-southern-gaza-as-preparations-for-cease-fire-talks-move-forward</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 10:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
